            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S) In nomine domini nostri Iehsu Chrisi eterni dei amen. Anno nativitate
                        eius millesimo centesimo nonagesimo secundo, sexto kalendas aprelis,
                        indictione decima. Ex huius instrumenti pateat recitatione quod nos
                                <persName><name ref="Albertinus">Albertinus</name></persName>
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Molestus">Molesti</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Obertus">Oibertus</name></persName> germanus et
                        quondam Molesti ambo simul pro nobis et pro <persName><name ref="Francus"
                                >Franco</name></persName> germano nostro vendimus et tradimus tibi
                                <persName><name ref="Rodelandus">Rolando</name></persName> confratri
                        hospitalis Altepascensis, recipienti pro domino <persName><name
                                ref="Aldebrandus">Aldibrando</name></persName> rectore dicti
                            <orgName key="#Hospitals" ref="#juridical_persons/3206"><rs
                                key="#Hospitals">hospitalis</rs>
                            <placeName key="#Hospitals" ref="#places/3207"
                            >Altepascensis</placeName></orgName>, unam nostram terre petiam que est
                        posita in plagis et finibus <placeName key="#Wine #Roads" ref="#places/3210"
                            >Putei</placeName> seu in loco ubi dicitur <rs key="#Wine">Vignale</rs>.
                        Que tenet unum caput in <rs key="#Roads">via publica</rs>, aliud in terra
                            <persName ref="#people/3217">Adimarii</persName> quondam <persName
                            ref="#people/3218">Alberti</persName> et <persName><name ref="Sardus"
                                >Sardi</name></persName> eius filii. Ambo latera tenet in terra
                        dicti hospitalis Altepascensis. Que est per mensuram stariora octo (…).
                            <foreign>Prezzo</foreign>: mille sol. bonorum denariorum pisani conii.
                            <foreign>Pena</foreign>: in duplum. (…) Actum apud <placeName
                            ref="#places/63">Sanctam Mariam ad Montem</placeName> et in <orgName
                            key="#Churches"><rs key="#Churches">ecclesia</rs> Sancti
                            Dalmatii</orgName>. Preterea suprascruptus Albertinus et Oibertus
                        germani in pignore dederunt et tradiderunt dicto Rolando, recipienti pro
                        supradicto Aldibrando, rectore dicti hospitali, unam terre petiam positam in
                            <placeName ref="#places/284">Petriolo</placeName>. Que tenet unum caput
                        in terra <persName><name ref="Berlingarius">Berlingarii</name></persName>
                        plebani et <persName><name ref="Riccia">Ricce</name></persName> uxoris
                                <persName><name ref="Rubacastellus">Rubacastelli</name></persName>
                        et quondam <persName><name ref="Corsus">Corsi</name></persName>. Caput aliud
                        tenet in terra ***, unum laterum tenet in terra <persName><name
                                ref="Hughicio">Uguicionis</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Widuccius">Guiducii</name></persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Hubaldus">Ubaldi</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Bernardus">Bernardi</name></persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Brunacianus">Bronaciani</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Dominicus">Dominici</name></persName>, aliud in
                        terra dicti Uguicionis. Que est stariora quatuor minus panori quatuor (…).
                            <foreign>Pena</foreign>: dupli. (…) <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Mainettus">Mainettus</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Bei">Bei</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Liutuldus">Litoldus</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Incalzatus">Incalciati</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Hugo">Ugolus</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Serotinus">Serotini</name></persName>.
                        Suprascripti rogati <rs key="#Witness">testes</rs> interfuerunt. (S) Ego
                            <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Leonardus"
                            >Leonardus</name></persName> domni imperatoris <rs key="#Notary"
                            >notarius</rs> post traditam scripsi, complevi et dedi.</ab>
